387}, {\"ngram\": \"the West\", \"from\": 2427, \"to\": 2435}, {\"ngram\": \"the Middle East\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Israel largely controls the media narrative of the war, falsely asserting that the violence began on Oct. 7.\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2587, \"end\": 2593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2893501127632374e-26, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the media narrative\", \"from\": 2611, \"to\": 2630}, {\"ngram\": \"the war\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2641}, {\"ngram\": \"the violence\", \"from\": 2666, \"to\": 2678}, {\"ngram\": \"Oct.\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2692}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Western news media has generally championed that narrative, carrying water for Israel.\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2786, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2696, \"end\": 2712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Western_News\", \"score\": 0.9999999902461241, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Western news\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Western_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Western_News\"}, {\"begin\": 2779, \"end\": 2785, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2893501127632374e-26, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that narrative\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2758}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 2769, \"to\": 2774}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Israel has engaged in a war not only against Hamas, but also against independent, mainly Arab journalists, killing more than 100 of those who have been reporting on the war from Gaza and who have not been embedded with Israel's military, which censors and controls content.The truth is that the Israeli carnage against Palestinians began long before the foundation of Hamas, which has its roots in an Israeli effort to undermine the rise of secular Palestinian nationalism in the 1970s.\", \"from\": 2787, \"to\": 3284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2798, \"end\": 2804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2893501127632374e-26, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 2843, \"end\": 2848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.459454071133863e-18, \"text\": \"Hamas\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\"}, {\"begin\": 2887, \"end\": 2891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 3.4004234795911878e-12, \"text\": \"Arab\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\"}, {\"begin\": 2976, \"end\": 2980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"score\": 0.9999998732469146, \"rank\": 1.2675314215609373e-07, \"text\": \"Gaza\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\"}, {\"begin\": 3017, \"end\": 3023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2893501127632374e-26, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 3093, \"end\": 3100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\", \"score\": 0.9512547129187126, \"rank\": 0.0